    "description": "Thanks to <a href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/jamesnewnorth/' target='_blank'>James Newnorth</a> (the founder of <a href='https://www.spelkollektivet.com/' target='_blank'>Spelkollektivet</a>) I went to the <a href='https://www.nordicgame.com/' target='_blank'>Nordic Game</a> conference. I took this Photos to help the Nordic Game Team to promote the event on social media channels while conference was just happening. It was a great experience and I was able to hear some amazing talks by <a href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Peter_Molyneux' target='_blank'>Peter Molyneux</a> and other great game designers as well."
